high_descs: Go forward, hang a left and go to the cabinet beneath the sink.
Take the glass out of the cabinet beneath the sink.
Turn around, go forward, hang a right and go to the microwave that is above the stove.
Put the glass inside the microwave and turn it on, remove the glass once it is hot.
Move to the right to the cabinet next to the microwave.
Put the glass inside the cabinet to the right of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot glass inside a cabinet.

high_descs: Walk up to the kitchen island, then hang a left and walk over to the sink.
Open the cabinet below the sink and take out the glass, then close the cabinet.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the oven and look up at the microwave.
Put the glass in the microwave and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds take the now heated glass out of the microwave.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the leftmost large upper cabinet door and put the heated glass inside to the right of the salt shaker, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated glass in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink on the left
Open the cupboard below the sink and get the glass
Turn around and go the stove on the right
Open the microwave door above the stove, put the glass inside next to the apple, close the door, turn the microwave on, open the microwave door, take out the glass, and close the microwave door
Go to the cupboard to the right of the microwave
Open the cupboard door, put the glass inside, and close the cupboard door
anns.task_desc: Put a glass away in the cupboard
